<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
 <head>
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
  <title>Welcome to Bid Aero <%="#{@company.name}"%></title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0;">
 <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" >
  <tr>
   <td>
     <table align="center" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="600" style="border: 1px solid #cccccc; ">
       <tr>
         <td align="center" bgcolor="#ffffff" style="padding: 20px 0 30px 0;">
         <%= email_image_tag("emailheaderblue.jpg") %>
         </td>
       </tr>
       <tr>
         <td bgcolor="#ffffff" style="padding: 40px 30px 40px 30px;">
           <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
            <tr>
             <td style="color: #153643; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;">
              Welcome to Bid Aero <b><%="#{@company.name}"%></b>
             </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
             <td style="padding: 20px 0 30px 0; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">
             Please click this link to complete your registration:
             <br>
             <br>
             <a href = "https://bid-aero.herokuapp.com/companies/confirm_email.<%="#{@company.confirm_token}" %>">Company Registration Link</a>
             <br>
             <br>
              Congratulations on joining Bid Aero, a truly revolitionary tool built for simplifying the buying and selling procees in the aviation industry.
             </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
             <td>
               <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
                <tr>
                 <td width="260" valign="top">
                  <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
                   <tr>
                    <td>
                    <%= email_image_tag("emailbuyicon.png") %>
                    </td>
                   </tr>
                   <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 25px 0 0 0; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px">
                     In this industry time is money.  You don't have time to sit around and send emails to receive quotes from multiple suppliers.  Using Bid Aero, you can simply search for any part that you need, and suppliers will compete against each other to give you the best possible deal.  Once you find the right part at the right price, your funds will be sent to our escrow account and will only be disbursed if you are completely happy with the part you received.
                    </td>
                   </tr>
                  </table>
                 </td>
                 <td style="font-size: 0; line-height: 0;" width="20">
                  &nbsp;
                 </td>
                 <td width="260" valign="top">
                  <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
                   <tr>
                    <td>
                    <%= email_image_tag("emailsellericon.png") %>
                    </td>
                   </tr>
                   <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 25px 0 0 0; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px">
                     As a seller, Bid Aero gives you a global reach and possibilities are endless.  You can now host your inventory completely free of charge and receive notifications when someone is searching for a part that you have in inventory.  You no longer have to worry about selling to customers who may not pay you.  Every time you make a sale, the buyer's funds will be held in an escrow account.  Once the verification is made, then you will prompted to ship the part.  
                    </td>
                   </tr>
                  </table>
                 </td>
                </tr>
               </table>
             </td>
            </tr>
           </table>
         </td>
       </tr>
       <tr>
         <td style="padding: 30px 30px 30px 30px;">
         <%= email_image_tag("bidaerofooter.jpg") %>
         </td>
       </tr>
     </table>
   </td>
  </tr>
 </table>
</body>
</html>



